‚∏ª

Why This System Exists

Most AI finance tools stop at:
	‚Ä¢	document Q&A
	‚Ä¢	retrieval-augmented chat
	‚Ä¢	static analysis scripts

They fail to address:
	‚Ä¢	institutional memory
	‚Ä¢	multi-agent specialization
	‚Ä¢	cross-company reasoning
	‚Ä¢	capital-level abstraction
	‚Ä¢	verification and auditability
	‚Ä¢	replay and learning over time

NotionWealth Intelligence was designed from the start as a decision platform, not a document tool.

‚∏ª

Example Workflows

Financial Research
	‚Ä¢	Ingest Apple, Microsoft, Google filings
	‚Ä¢	Analyze revenue drivers and growth
	‚Ä¢	Attach sources and evidence
	‚Ä¢	Persist as a research session

Risk & Anomaly Analysis
	‚Ä¢	Compare risk language across years
	‚Ä¢	Detect regulatory clustering
	‚Ä¢	Identify financial irregularities
	‚Ä¢	Flag emerging threats

Competitive Intelligence
	‚Ä¢	Cross-company metric normalization
	‚Ä¢	Strategic positioning analysis
	‚Ä¢	Advantage and vulnerability mapping

Portfolio Strategy
	‚Ä¢	Exposure and concentration analysis
	‚Ä¢	Correlated risk detection
	‚Ä¢	Capital posture construction

Capital Allocation
	‚Ä¢	Scenario modeling
	‚Ä¢	Growth vs risk tradeoffs
	‚Ä¢	Rebalancing logic
	‚Ä¢	Decision memos

Research Replay
	‚Ä¢	Reload historical research
	‚Ä¢	Re-run with new data
	‚Ä¢	Diff outputs
	‚Ä¢	Track reasoning evolution

