‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ scripts/             # test and execution scripts
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ docs/                # architecture and design notes
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ mcp_server.py        # agent tool server


‚∏ª

Running the System

1. Install dependencies

pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Add API key

Create .env:

GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_key_here

3. Ingest documents

Place PDFs into:

data/raw/

Run ingestion or use UI.

‚∏ª

4. Start MCP server

python mcp_server.py


‚∏ª

5. Launch UI

streamlit run finance-agent/ui/app.py


‚∏ª

Research Artifacts

Every research run generates:
	‚Ä¢	a structured research session
	‚Ä¢	evidence links
	‚Ä¢	agent execution traces
	‚Ä¢	optional replay capability

This enables:
	‚Ä¢	auditability
	‚Ä¢	verification
	‚Ä¢	institutional learning
	‚Ä¢	decision history

‚∏ª

Design Philosophy
	‚Ä¢	Agents are specialists, not prompts
	‚Ä¢	Memory is stratified, not flat
	‚Ä¢	Verification is mandatory
	‚Ä¢	Traces are first-class artifacts
	‚Ä¢	Replay is a core system primitive
	‚Ä¢	Outputs are decision surfaces, not answers

